short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find out which website builder may have been used to build a site.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Ever wondered which website builder was used to build a site? This extension will tell you automatically. Just start browsing, and this extension glances at the source code to identify telltale signs of specific website builders. Currently supports WordPress, Wix, Weebly, Webflow, Unbounce, Swipe Pages, Squarespace, Shopify, Readymag, Leadpages, Kajabi, HubSpot, Gatsby, Docusaurus, ConvertKit, and ClickFunnels.
